#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[20];
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(1) uniform UnityPerDraw {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LODFade;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightData;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_LightIndices[2];
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_ProbesOcclusion;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SpecCube0_HDR;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_LightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM vec4 unity_DynamicLightmapST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHAb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBr;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBg;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHBb;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 unity_SHC;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FurTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emissive;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _EmisssionScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _InvRim;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cull;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ZWrite;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ZTest;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AlphaToMask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SrcBlendFactor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DstBlendFactor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SrcBlendFactorAlpha;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DstBlendFactorAlpha;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BlendOp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BlendOpAlpha;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Metallic;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMin;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMax;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampThreshold;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampSmooth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FurDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FurAOCol;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _Frequency;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _Amplitude;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _WaveLength;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Power;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat11;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _FurTex_ST.xy + _FurTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat0.y * u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat11 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = max(u_xlat1.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_2.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_RampThreshold, _RampThreshold, _RampThreshold)) + _FurDir.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * vec3(0.25, 0.25, 0.25) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat3.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat3.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat3.zzz + u_xlat3.xyw;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat3.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat1.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat3.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat3.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat3.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat3.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat3.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat3.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 300 es
#ifdef GL_EXT_shader_texture_lod
#extension GL_EXT_shader_texture_lod : enable
#endif

precision highp float;
precision highp int;
#define HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS 1
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
#define UNITY_UNIFORM
#else
#define UNITY_UNIFORM uniform
#endif
#define UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION 1
#if UNITY_SUPPORTS_UNIFORM_LOCATION
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x) layout(location = x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(binding = x, std140)
#else
#define UNITY_LOCATION(x)
#define UNITY_BINDING(x) layout(std140)
#endif
uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowOffset0;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowOffset1;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowOffset2;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowOffset3;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowParams;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FurTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emissive;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _EmisssionScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _InvRim;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cull;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ZWrite;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ZTest;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AlphaToMask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SrcBlendFactor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DstBlendFactor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SrcBlendFactorAlpha;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DstBlendFactorAlpha;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BlendOp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BlendOpAlpha;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Metallic;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMin;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMax;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampThreshold;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampSmooth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FurDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FurAOCol;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _Frequency;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _Amplitude;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _WaveLength;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Power;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
bool u_xlatb5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.zw).x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-_SketchHalftoneMax) * 0.25 + u_xlat16_0.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(u_xlat16_1.x<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_1.x<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat0.xy,u_xlat0.z);
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat2.xy,u_xlat2.z);
    u_xlat0.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat2.xy,u_xlat2.z);
    u_xlat0.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat2.xy,u_xlat2.z);
    u_xlat0.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat0, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_6.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb5 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb5 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb5 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_6.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_3.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_3.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_3.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = _NormalScale;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_11 = max(u_xlat16_11, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_11 = min(u_xlat16_11, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_11 = (-u_xlat16_11) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.xz = u_xlat16_6.xx * u_xlat16_3.xy;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_16 = min(max(u_xlat16_16, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_16 = clamp(u_xlat16_16, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_6.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = log2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x * _RimlightScale;
    u_xlat16_6.x = exp2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(u_xlat16_6.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_16) * 2.0 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x * _InvRim + u_xlat16_16;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_16) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = _RimlightColor.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _FurAOCol.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * _FurAOCol.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.25, 0.25, 0.25) + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.20000005, 2.20000005, 2.20000005);
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "ENABLE_POST_TONE" "_MAIN_LIGHT_SHADOWS" "_SHADOWS_SOFT" }
"// hash: cea058bed2dfe927
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[20];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _FurTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _SHScale;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
uniform 	mediump float _RampThreshold;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _FurDir;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat11;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _FurTex_ST.xy + _FurTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat0.y * u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat11 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = max(u_xlat1.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_2.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_RampThreshold, _RampThreshold, _RampThreshold)) + _FurDir.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * vec3(0.25, 0.25, 0.25) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat3.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat3.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat3.zzz + u_xlat3.xyw;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat3.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat1.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat3.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat3.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat3.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat3.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat3.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat3.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif
precision highp int;
uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowOffset0;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowOffset1;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowOffset2;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowOffset3;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowParams;
uniform 	mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
uniform 	mediump float _NormalScale;
uniform 	mediump float _InvRim;
uniform 	mediump float _RimlightScale;
uniform 	mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
uniform 	mediump float _SketchHalftoneMax;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _FurAOCol;
uniform lowp sampler2D _MainTex;
uniform lowp sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
uniform highp sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
uniform lowp sampler2D _FurTex;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
vec4 u_xlat0;
lowp vec3 u_xlat10_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_2;
bool u_xlatb2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
bool u_xlatb5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.x = texture2D(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.zw).x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-_SketchHalftoneMax) * 0.25 + u_xlat10_0.x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_1.x<0.0;
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat0.xy).x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x<u_xlat0.z;
    u_xlat0.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlat2.x<u_xlat2.z;
    u_xlat0.y = (u_xlatb2) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlat2.x<u_xlat2.z;
    u_xlat0.z = (u_xlatb2) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlat2.x<u_xlat2.z;
    u_xlat0.w = (u_xlatb2) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat0, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlatb5 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb5 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_6.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_3.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_3.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_3.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = _NormalScale;
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_2 = texture2D(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat10_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_11 = max(u_xlat16_11, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_11 = min(u_xlat16_11, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_11 = (-u_xlat16_11) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.xz = u_xlat16_6.xx * u_xlat16_3.xy;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat16_16 = clamp(u_xlat16_16, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_6.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = log2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x * _RimlightScale;
    u_xlat16_6.x = exp2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(u_xlat16_6.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_16) * 2.0 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x * _InvRim + u_xlat16_16;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_16) * u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = _RimlightColor.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _FurAOCol.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * _FurAOCol.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.25, 0.25, 0.25) + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.20000005, 2.20000005, 2.20000005);
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat11;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _FurTex_ST.xy + _FurTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat0.y * u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat11 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = max(u_xlat1.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_2.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_RampThreshold, _RampThreshold, _RampThreshold)) + _FurDir.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * vec3(0.25, 0.25, 0.25) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat3.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat3.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat3.zzz + u_xlat3.xyw;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat3.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat1.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat3.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat3.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat3.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat3.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat3.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat3.zzzz + u_xlat0;

uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowOffset1;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowOffset2;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowOffset3;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightShadowParams;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FurTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emissive;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _EmisssionScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _InvRim;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cull;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ZWrite;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _ZTest;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _AlphaToMask;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SrcBlendFactor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DstBlendFactor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SrcBlendFactorAlpha;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _DstBlendFactorAlpha;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BlendOp;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _BlendOpAlpha;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Metallic;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cutoff;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMin;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SketchHalftoneMax;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampThreshold;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RampSmooth;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FurDir;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FurAOCol;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _Frequency;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _Amplitude;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _WaveLength;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Power;
#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
};
#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2DShadow hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(3) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(4) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec4 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
bool u_xlatb5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.zw).x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-_SketchHalftoneMax) * 0.25 + u_xlat16_0.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(u_xlat16_1.x<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_1.x<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    vec3 txVec0 = vec3(u_xlat0.xy,u_xlat0.z);
    u_xlat0.x = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec0, 0.0);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    vec3 txVec1 = vec3(u_xlat2.xy,u_xlat2.z);
    u_xlat0.y = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec1, 0.0);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    vec3 txVec2 = vec3(u_xlat2.xy,u_xlat2.z);
    u_xlat0.z = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec2, 0.0);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    vec3 txVec3 = vec3(u_xlat2.xy,u_xlat2.z);
    u_xlat0.w = textureLod(hlslcc_zcmp_MainLightShadowmapTexture, txVec3, 0.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat0, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_6.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
#endif
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb5 = !!(vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0);
#else
    u_xlatb5 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
#endif
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb5 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_6.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_3.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_3.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_3.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = _NormalScale;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_11 = max(u_xlat16_11, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_11 = min(u_xlat16_11, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_11 = (-u_xlat16_11) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.xz = u_xlat16_6.xx * u_xlat16_3.xy;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(max(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_16 = min(max(u_xlat16_16, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_16 = clamp(u_xlat16_16, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_6.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = log2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x * _RimlightScale;
    u_xlat16_6.x = exp2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(u_xlat16_6.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_16) * 2.0 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x * _InvRim + u_xlat16_16;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_16) * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = _RimlightColor.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _FurAOCol.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * _FurAOCol.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.25, 0.25, 0.25) + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(0.155000001, 0.155000001, 0.155000001);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz / u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.01900005, 1.01900005, 1.01900005);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = log2(u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.20000005, 2.20000005, 2.20000005);
    SV_Target0.xyz = exp2(u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}
SubProgram "gles " {
Keywords { "_MAIN_LIGHT_SHADOWS" "_SHADOWS_SOFT" }
"// hash: d55c97b0a3a86e39
#ifdef VERTEX
#version 100

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[4];
uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[20];
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _FurTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _SHScale;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
uniform 	mediump float _RampThreshold;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _FurDir;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat11;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _FurTex_ST.xy + _FurTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat0.y * u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat11 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = max(u_xlat1.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_2.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_RampThreshold, _RampThreshold, _RampThreshold)) + _FurDir.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * vec3(0.25, 0.25, 0.25) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat3.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat3.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat3.zzz + u_xlat3.xyw;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat3.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat1.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat3.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[0] * u_xlat3.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[2] * u_xlat3.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    vs_TEXCOORD7 = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4_MainLightWorldToShadow[3];
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat3.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat3.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat3.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH

precision highp int;

uniform 	mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;

uniform lowp sampler2D _BumpMapNr;

uniform lowp sampler2D _FurTex;

varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD7;

vec4 u_xlat0;
lowp vec3 u_xlat10_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_1;
vec3 u_xlat2;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_2;
bool u_xlatb2;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
bool u_xlatb5;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.x = texture2D(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.zw).x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-_SketchHalftoneMax) * 0.25 + u_xlat10_0.x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_1.x<0.0;
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    u_xlat0.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset0.xyz;
    u_xlat0.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat0.xy).x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat0.x<u_xlat0.z;
    u_xlat0.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset1.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlat2.x<u_xlat2.z;
    u_xlat0.y = (u_xlatb2) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset2.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlat2.x<u_xlat2.z;
    u_xlat0.z = (u_xlatb2) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat2.xyz = vs_TEXCOORD7.xyz + _MainLightShadowOffset3.xyz;
    u_xlat2.x = texture2D(_MainLightShadowmapTexture, u_xlat2.xy).x;
    u_xlatb2 = u_xlat2.x<u_xlat2.z;
    u_xlat0.w = (u_xlatb2) ? 0.0 : 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat0, vec4(0.25, 0.25, 0.25, 0.25));
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-_MainLightShadowParams.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * _MainLightShadowParams.x + u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlatb0 = 0.0>=vs_TEXCOORD7.z;
    u_xlatb5 = vs_TEXCOORD7.z>=1.0;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlatb5 || u_xlatb0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (u_xlatb0) ? 1.0 : u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-_RimlightShadowScale) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_6.x + _RimlightShadowScale;
    u_xlat16_3.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_3.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_3.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = _NormalScale;
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_2 = texture2D(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat10_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_11 = max(u_xlat16_11, 0.0399999991);

    u_xlat16_11 = (-u_xlat16_11) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.xz = u_xlat16_6.xx * u_xlat16_3.xy;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyw = u_xlat16_6.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_3.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyw;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat16_3.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xxx * u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.x = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_6.x = clamp(u_xlat16_6.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_3.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat16_16 = clamp(u_xlat16_16, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_6.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = log2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x * _RimlightScale;
    u_xlat16_6.x = exp2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(u_xlat16_6.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_1.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_16) * 2.0 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x * _InvRim + u_xlat16_16;
    u_xlat16_1.x = u_xlat16_6.x * u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_16) * u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_6.xyz * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = _RimlightColor.xyz * u_xlat16_1.xxx + u_xlat16_6.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _FurAOCol.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * _FurAOCol.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.25, 0.25, 0.25) + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(0.155000001, 0.155000001, 0.155000001);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz / u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.01900005, 1.01900005, 1.01900005);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = log2(u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.20000005, 2.20000005, 2.20000005);
    SV_Target0.xyz = exp2(u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#endif
"
}

#ifdef VERTEX

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

uniform 	vec4 hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[4];
uniform 	mediump vec4 unity_WorldTransformParams;

uniform 	mediump vec4 _FurTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _SHScale;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
uniform 	mediump float _RampThreshold;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _FurDir;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
vec4 u_xlat0;

mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;

mediump vec2 u_xlat16_2;

float u_xlat6;

void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _FurTex_ST.xy + _FurTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat0.y * u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat11 + 0.125;

    u_xlat3.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat3.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat3.zzz + u_xlat3.xyw;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat3.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat1.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);

    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;

    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;

    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat3.xxxx + u_xlat0;

    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _FurTex_ST.xy + _FurTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat0.y * u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat11 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = max(u_xlat1.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_2.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_RampThreshold, _RampThreshold, _RampThreshold)) + _FurDir.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat3.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat3.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat3.zzz + u_xlat3.xyw;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat3.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat1.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat3.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat3.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat3.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#if HLSLCC_ENABLE_UNIFORM_BUFFERS
UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FurTex_ST;

#endif
UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.zw).x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-_SketchHalftoneMax) * 0.449999988 + u_xlat16_0.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(u_xlat16_1.x<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_1.x<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    u_xlat16_1.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_1.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_1.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _NormalScale;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(u_xlat16_3.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xx * u_xlat16_6.xy;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_16 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_16);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_16) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_16 = min(max(u_xlat16_16, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_16 = clamp(u_xlat16_16, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_16) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = log2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x * _RimlightScale;
    u_xlat16_6.x = exp2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(u_xlat16_6.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_11 = (-u_xlat16_1.x) * 2.0 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_11 * _InvRim + u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xzw * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = _RimlightColor.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xxx + u_xlat16_1.xzw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _FurAOCol.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * _FurAOCol.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988) + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(0.155000001, 0.155000001, 0.155000001);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz / u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.01900005, 1.01900005, 1.01900005);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = log2(u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.20000005, 2.20000005, 2.20000005);
    SV_Target0.xyz = exp2(u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

#ifdef VERTEX

varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;

{

    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat6);

    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_1;

    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;

precision highp int;
uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;

varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;

varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
vec3 u_xlat0;
lowp vec3 u_xlat10_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
void main()
{

    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_1.x<0.0;
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}

    u_xlat16_1.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_1.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);

    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_16 = clamp(u_xlat16_16, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_16) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = log2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x * _RimlightScale;
    u_xlat16_6.x = exp2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(u_xlat16_6.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_11 = (-u_xlat16_1.x) * 2.0 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_11 * _InvRim + u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xzw * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = _RimlightColor.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xxx + u_xlat16_1.xzw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _FurAOCol.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * _FurAOCol.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988) + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    SV_Target0.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.20000005, 2.20000005, 2.20000005);
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

UNITY_BINDING(0) uniform UnityPerMaterial {
#endif
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _MainTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _FurTex_ST;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Emissive;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SpecularColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _MetallicOffset;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _NormalScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _EmisssionScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _SHScale;

	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _InvRim;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _RimlightShadowScale;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
	UNITY_UNIFORM mediump float _Cull;

};
#endif
in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat11;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _FurTex_ST.xy + _FurTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat0.y * u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat11 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = max(u_xlat1.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_2.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_RampThreshold, _RampThreshold, _RampThreshold)) + _FurDir.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat3.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat3.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat3.zzz + u_xlat3.xyw;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat3.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat1.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat3.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat3.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat3.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

UNITY_LOCATION(0) uniform mediump sampler2D _MainTex;
UNITY_LOCATION(1) uniform mediump sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
UNITY_LOCATION(2) uniform mediump sampler2D _FurTex;
in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
layout(location = 0) out mediump vec4 SV_Target0;
vec3 u_xlat0;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.zw).x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-_SketchHalftoneMax) * 0.449999988 + u_xlat16_0.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(u_xlat16_1.x<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_1.x<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    u_xlat16_1.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_1.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_1.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _NormalScale;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(u_xlat16_3.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xx * u_xlat16_6.xy;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_16 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_16);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_16) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_16 = min(max(u_xlat16_16, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_16 = clamp(u_xlat16_16, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_16) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = log2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x * _RimlightScale;
    u_xlat16_6.x = exp2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(u_xlat16_6.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_11 = (-u_xlat16_1.x) * 2.0 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_11 * _InvRim + u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);

    u_xlat16_1.xyz = _RimlightColor.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xxx + u_xlat16_1.xzw;

uniform 	mediump vec4 _FurTex_ST;
uniform 	mediump float _SHScale;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHTopColor;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _SHBotColor;
uniform 	mediump float _RampThreshold;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _FurDir;
attribute highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
attribute highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
attribute highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
attribute highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat11;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _FurTex_ST.xy + _FurTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat0.y * u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat11 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = max(u_xlat1.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_2.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_RampThreshold, _RampThreshold, _RampThreshold)) + _FurDir.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat3.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat3.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat3.zzz + u_xlat3.xyw;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat3.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat1.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat3.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat3.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat3.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;
}

#endif
#ifdef FRAGMENT
#version 100

#ifdef GL_FRAGMENT_PRECISION_HIGH
    precision highp float;
#else
    precision mediump float;
#endif
precision highp int;
uniform 	vec4 _MainLightPosition;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _MainLightColor;
uniform 	mediump float _RoughNessOffset;
uniform 	mediump float _NormalScale;
uniform 	mediump float _InvRim;
uniform 	mediump float _RimlightScale;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _RimlightColor;
uniform 	mediump float _SketchHalftoneMax;
uniform 	mediump vec4 _FurAOCol;
uniform lowp sampler2D _MainTex;
uniform lowp sampler2D _BumpMapNr;
uniform lowp sampler2D _FurTex;
varying highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
varying mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
#define SV_Target0 gl_FragData[0]
vec3 u_xlat0;
lowp vec3 u_xlat10_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
lowp vec4 u_xlat10_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;
mediump float u_xlat16_11;
mediump float u_xlat16_16;
void main()
{
    u_xlat10_0.x = texture2D(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.zw).x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-_SketchHalftoneMax) * 0.449999988 + u_xlat10_0.x;
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_1.x<0.0;
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    u_xlat16_1.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_1.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_1.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _NormalScale;
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat10_2 = texture2D(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat10_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat10_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(u_xlat16_3.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xx * u_xlat16_6.xy;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_16 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_16);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_16) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat16_16 = clamp(u_xlat16_16, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_16) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = log2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x * _RimlightScale;
    u_xlat16_6.x = exp2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(u_xlat16_6.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_11 = (-u_xlat16_1.x) * 2.0 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_11 * _InvRim + u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat10_0.xyz = texture2D(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat10_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat10_0.xyz * vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xzw * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = _RimlightColor.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xxx + u_xlat16_1.xzw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _FurAOCol.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * _FurAOCol.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988) + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(0.155000001, 0.155000001, 0.155000001);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz / u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.01900005, 1.01900005, 1.01900005);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = log2(u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.20000005, 2.20000005, 2.20000005);
    SV_Target0.xyz = exp2(u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;
out highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
out highp vec3 vs_TEXCOORD2;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;
out mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD6;
vec4 u_xlat0;
vec4 u_xlat1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;
float u_xlat6;
float u_xlat11;
float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _FurTex_ST.xy + _FurTex_ST.zw;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[0].xyz);
    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat0.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat0.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat0.y * u_xlat0.y;
    u_xlat6 = u_xlat0.y * 0.25;
    u_xlat11 = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + u_xlat6;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat1.x * 0.125 + (-u_xlat6);
    u_xlat1.y = u_xlat1.x + 0.125;
    u_xlat1.x = u_xlat11 + 0.125;
    u_xlat16_2.xy = max(u_xlat1.xy, vec2(0.0, 0.0));
    u_xlat16_2.xy = u_xlat16_2.xy * vec2(vec2(_SHScale, _SHScale));
    u_xlat16_1 = u_xlat16_2.yyyy * _SHBotColor;
    vs_TEXCOORD1 = u_xlat16_2.xxxx * _SHTopColor + u_xlat16_1;
    u_xlat3.xyz = in_NORMAL0.xyz * vec3(vec3(_RampThreshold, _RampThreshold, _RampThreshold)) + _FurDir.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988) + in_POSITION0.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat3.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyw = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * u_xlat3.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat3.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * u_xlat3.zzz + u_xlat3.xyw;
    u_xlat3.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[3].xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD2.xyz = u_xlat3.xyz;
    u_xlat1.xyw = (-u_xlat3.xyz) + _WorldSpaceCameraPos.xyz;
    u_xlat0.w = u_xlat1.x;
    vs_TEXCOORD3 = u_xlat0;
    u_xlat4.xyz = in_TANGENT0.yyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[1].xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[0].xyz * in_TANGENT0.xxx + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat4.xyz = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_ObjectToWorld[2].xyz * in_TANGENT0.zzz + u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat15 = dot(u_xlat4.xyz, u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = max(u_xlat15, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat15 = inversesqrt(u_xlat15);
    u_xlat2.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat4.xyz;
    u_xlat2.w = u_xlat1.y;
    vs_TEXCOORD4 = u_xlat2;
    u_xlat4.xyz = u_xlat0.zxy * u_xlat2.yzx;
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.yzx * u_xlat2.zxy + (-u_xlat4.xyz);
    u_xlat15 = in_TANGENT0.w * unity_WorldTransformParams.w;
    u_xlat1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat15) * u_xlat0.xyz;
    vs_TEXCOORD5 = u_xlat1;
    vs_TEXCOORD6 = vec4(0.0, 0.0, 0.0, 0.0);
    u_xlat0 = u_xlat3.yyyy * hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[1];
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[0] * u_xlat3.xxxx + u_xlat0;
    u_xlat0 = hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[2] * u_xlat3.zzzz + u_xlat0;
    gl_Position = u_xlat0 + hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_MatrixVP[3];
    return;

in highp vec4 vs_TEXCOORD0;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD1;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD3;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD4;
in mediump vec4 vs_TEXCOORD5;

mediump vec3 u_xlat16_0;
bool u_xlatb0;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
mediump vec4 u_xlat16_2;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_3;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_4;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_6;
mediump vec3 u_xlat16_8;

mediump float u_xlat16_16;
void main()
{
    u_xlat16_0.x = texture(_FurTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.zw).x;
    u_xlat16_1.x = (-_SketchHalftoneMax) * 0.449999988 + u_xlat16_0.x;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlatb0 = !!(u_xlat16_1.x<0.0);
#else
    u_xlatb0 = u_xlat16_1.x<0.0;
#endif
    if(u_xlatb0){discard;}
    u_xlat16_1.x = vs_TEXCOORD3.w;
    u_xlat16_1.y = vs_TEXCOORD4.w;
    u_xlat16_1.z = vs_TEXCOORD5.w;
    u_xlat0.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat0.x = max(u_xlat0.x, 1.17549435e-38);
    u_xlat0.x = inversesqrt(u_xlat0.x);
    u_xlat0.xyz = u_xlat0.xxx * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.x = _NormalScale;
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_2 = texture(_BumpMapNr, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy);
    u_xlat16_6.xyz = u_xlat16_2.xyz * vec3(2.0, 2.0, 2.0) + vec3(-1.0, -1.0, -1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = u_xlat16_2.w + _RoughNessOffset;
    u_xlat16_3.x = max(u_xlat16_3.x, 0.0399999991);
    u_xlat16_3.x = min(u_xlat16_3.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_3.x = (-u_xlat16_3.x) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_1.xy = u_xlat16_1.xx * u_xlat16_6.xy;
    u_xlat16_8.xyz = u_xlat16_1.yyy * vs_TEXCOORD5.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xxx * vs_TEXCOORD4.xyz + u_xlat16_8.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_6.zzz * vs_TEXCOORD3.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_16 = inversesqrt(u_xlat16_16);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = vec3(u_xlat16_16) * u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_16 = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, u_xlat0.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_16 = min(max(u_xlat16_16, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_16 = clamp(u_xlat16_16, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_1.x = dot(u_xlat16_1.xyz, _MainLightPosition.xyz);
#ifdef UNITY_ADRENO_ES3
    u_xlat16_1.x = min(max(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0), 1.0);
#else
    u_xlat16_1.x = clamp(u_xlat16_1.x, 0.0, 1.0);
#endif
    u_xlat16_6.x = (-u_xlat16_16) + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_6.x = log2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_6.x * _RimlightScale;
    u_xlat16_6.x = exp2(u_xlat16_6.x);
    u_xlat16_6.x = min(u_xlat16_6.x, 1.0);
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_3.x * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_11 = (-u_xlat16_1.x) * 2.0 + 1.0;
    u_xlat16_11 = u_xlat16_11 * _InvRim + u_xlat16_1.x;
    u_xlat16_6.x = u_xlat16_11 * u_xlat16_6.x;
    u_xlat16_0.xyz = texture(_MainTex, vs_TEXCOORD0.xy).xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xxx * u_xlat16_0.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_0.xyz * vs_TEXCOORD1.xyz;
    u_xlat0.xyz = _MainLightPosition.www * _MainLightColor.xyz;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = u_xlat0.xyz * _MainLightColor.www;
    u_xlat16_4.xyz = min(u_xlat16_4.xyz, _MainLightColor.www);
    u_xlat16_1.xzw = u_xlat16_1.xzw * u_xlat16_4.xyz + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = _RimlightColor.xyz * u_xlat16_6.xxx + u_xlat16_1.xzw;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * _FurAOCol.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = (-u_xlat16_1.xyz) * _FurAOCol.xyz + u_xlat16_1.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(0.449999988, 0.449999988, 0.449999988) + u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_3.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz + vec3(0.155000001, 0.155000001, 0.155000001);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz / u_xlat16_3.xyz;
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(1.01900005, 1.01900005, 1.01900005);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = log2(u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    u_xlat16_1.xyz = u_xlat16_1.xyz * vec3(2.20000005, 2.20000005, 2.20000005);
    SV_Target0.xyz = exp2(u_xlat16_1.xyz);
    SV_Target0.w = 1.0;
    return;
}

uniform 	vec3 _WorldSpaceCameraPos;

in highp vec4 in_POSITION0;
in highp vec3 in_NORMAL0;
in highp vec4 in_TANGENT0;
in highp vec2 in_TEXCOORD0;

mediump vec4 u_xlat16_1;
vec4 u_xlat2;
mediump vec2 u_xlat16_2;
vec4 u_xlat3;
vec3 u_xlat4;

float u_xlat15;
void main()
{
    vs_TEXCOORD0.xy = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _MainTex_ST.xy + _MainTex_ST.zw;
    vs_TEXCOORD0.zw = in_TEXCOORD0.xy * _FurTex_ST.xy + _FurTex_ST.zw;

    u_xlat0.y = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[1].xyz);
    u_xlat0.z = dot(in_NORMAL0.xyz, hlslcc_mtx4x4unity_WorldToObject[2].xyz);
